      'PRODIGE 7 challenged oxaliplatin HIPEC specifically — it did NOT invalidate mitomycin C-based HIPEC. The Verwaal RCT used MMC and demonstrated robust OS benefit (median OS 22.3 vs 12.6 months). Do not extrapolate PRODIGE 7 negativity to MMC protocols.',
