      'BAP1 loss in peritoneal mesothelioma paradoxically indicates BETTER prognosis (opposite of pleural) — BAP1-mutated MPeM achieves median OS not reached at 5 years vs 28 months for BAP1-intact tumours (MSKCC cohort).',
