    patient_selection: 'ESMO 2023 / OVHIPEC-1 criteria for interval CRS+HIPEC: ECOG 0–1, stage III epithelial ovarian cancer (HGSOC primary target), complete or partial clinical response after NACT × 3 cycles (carboplatin+paclitaxel), technical feasibility of CC-0/CC-1. No parenchymal liver metastases, no extensive upper abdominal disease precluding CC-0, no distant metastases. BRCA1/2 status does not alter CRS+HIPEC indication but directs postoperative maintenance. Fagotti laparoscopic score >8 predicts inability to achieve CC-0 in >80% — mandates NACT first. AGO score positive = good operability predictor. OVHIPEC-2 (NCT03772028): evaluating HIPEC at primary debulking (upfront) surgery.',
