      'HER2 amplification rate in SBA (~15%) is 5-fold higher than in CRC (~3%) — HER2 testing is mandatory on all SBA specimens, especially when considering systemic therapy regimen selection.',
      'For CRS+HIPEC in SBA-PM, extrapolate from CRC selection criteria (PCI ≤15, CC-0/1 achievable) with caution — no SBA-specific RCTs exist and small bowel mesentery involvement is harder to resect than colonic PM. Registry enrolment is strongly encouraged.',
