    pipac_indication: 'Same as ovarian cancer — cisplatin 7.5 mg/m² + doxorubicin 1.5 mg/m² for unresectable or recurrent disease. PIPAC-OPC protocol. Ascites control and palliative disease reduction in platinum-resistant recurrence.',
