    follow_up: 'Same as ovarian cancer — CA125 every 3 months for 2 years, CT every 6 months for 2 years then annually. BRCA genetic counselling for patient and first-degree relatives. Annual surveillance for BRCA-related cancers (breast, pancreatic). For BRCA-positive patients who underwent prophylactic BSO and develop PPC: reassess timing of prophylactic mastectomy discussion with breast oncology.',
